 r‚Üêlevel Help Cmd;ref;‚éïTRAP
 r‚Üê''
 :Select level
 :Case 0
     :Select ‚éïC Cmd
     :Case ‚éïC'Add'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ']APLGit2.add <filter> -project='
     :Case ‚éïC'AddGitIgnore'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ']APLGit2.AddGitIgnore [space|folder]'
     :Case ‚éïC'ChangeLog <apl-name> -project='
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ']APLGit2.ChangeLog <filter> -project='
     :Case ‚éïC'Commit'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ']APLGit2.Commit [space|folder] -m= -add -amend'
     :Case ‚éïC'CompareCommits'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ']APLGit2.CompareCommits [hash1] [hash2] -project= -use=[name|?] -view'
     :Case ‚éïC'CurrentBranch'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ']APLGit2.CurrenBranch [space|folder]'
     :Case ‚éïC'Diff'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ']APLGit2.Diff [space|folder] -verbose'
     :Case ‚éïC'GetTagOfLatestRelease'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ']APLGit2.GetTagOfLatestRelease [space|folder]'
     :Case ‚éïC'Init'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ']APLGit2.Init [folder] -quiet'
     :Case ‚éïC'IsDirty'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ']APLGit2.IsDirty [space|folder]'
     :Case ‚éïC'IsGitProject'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ']APLGit2.IsGitProject [space|folder]'
     :Case ‚éïC'ListBranches'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ']APLGit2.ListBranches [space|folder] -a -r'
     :Case ‚éïC'Log'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ']APLGit2.Log [space|folder] -since= -verbose -max= -name='
     :Case ‚éïC'NoOfUntrackedFiles'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ']APLGit2.NoOfUntrackedFiles [space|folder]'
     :Case ‚éïC'OpenGitShell'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ']APLGit2.OpenGitShell [space|folder]'
     :Case ‚éïC'RefLog'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ']APLGit2.RefLog [space|folder] -max= -all -branch= -project='
     :Case ‚éïC'Status'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ']APLGit2.Status -short -path='
     :Case ‚éïC'StashApply'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ']APLGit2.StashApply [space|folder] -n=<number of stash>'
     :Case ‚éïC'StashClear'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ']APLGit2.StashClear [space|folder]'
     :Case ‚éïC'StashDrop'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ']APLGit2.StashDrop [space|folder] -n='
     :Case ‚éïC'StashList'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ']APLGit2.StashList [space|folder]'
     :Case ‚éïC'StashPop'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ']APLGit2.StashPop [space|folder] -n='
     :Case ‚éïC'StashPush'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ']APLGit2.StashPush [space|folder]'
     :Case ‚éïC'StashShow'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ']APLGit2.StashShow [space|folder] [n]'
     :Case ‚éïC'Squash'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ']APLGit2.Squash [space|folder] [noOf] -m=<message>'
     :Case ‚éïC'Version'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ']APLGit2.Version'
     :Else
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ'There is no help available'
     :EndSelect
     :If 'Version'‚â¢Cmd
         r,‚Üê''(']APLGit2.',Cmd,' -?? ‚çù Enter this for more information ')
     :EndIf

 :Case 1
     ('No second-level help found for ',Cmd)Assert 0<help.‚éïNC Cmd
     r‚Üêhelp‚çéCmd
 :Case 2
     ('No third-level help found for ',Cmd)Assert 0<help.‚éïNC Cmd
     :Select ‚éïC Cmd
     :CaseList ‚éïC¬®'Add' ''
         r,‚ÜêAddProjectOptions 1
     :Else
         r,‚ÜêAddProjectOptions 0
     :EndSelect

 :EndSelect
